<paragraph id="IFRS07_B9"><paranum>B9</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 7"/><data name="paranum" value="B9"/></prolog><body><variant base="F36666117" id="IFRS07_B9_V2" principles="no"> <p id="IFRS07_P1037"><xref base="F51887444" href="IFRS07_35K.dita#IFRS07_35K" id="IFRS07_X0931">Paragraphs 35K(a)</xref> and <xref base="F51887445" href="IFRS07_36.dita#IFRS07_36/IFRS07_36_V2" id="IFRS07_X0932">36(a)</xref> require disclosure of the amount that best represents the entity&#x2019;s maximum exposure to <xref base="SL144807" href="IFRS07_APPA.dita#IFRS07_APPA/IFRS07_P0862">credit risk<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0064"/></ph></xref>. For a <xref base="SL37522973" href="../ias32/IAS32_11.dita#IAS32_11/IAS32_P0115">financial asset<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0123"/></ph></xref>, this is typically the gross carrying amount, net of:</p> <ol base="SL36666121" id="IFRS07_L0125" type="lower-alpha"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value> <p base="SL36666123" id="IFRS07_P1038">any amounts offset in accordance with <xref base="F77793513" href="../ias32/IAS32_TOC.dita#IAS32_TOC0001/IAS32_TOC0001_V2" id="IFRS07_X0933">IAS 32</xref>; and</p> </li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value> <p base="SL36666128" id="IFRS07_P1040">any loss allowance recognised in accordance with <xref base="F43753028" href="../ifrs09/IFRS09_TOC.dita#IFRS09_TOC0001/IFRS09_TOC0001_V1" id="IFRS07_X0935">IFRS 9</xref>.</p> </li></ol></variant></body></paragraph>